### ============================
### VERSION 1 - Client-Server Basic
### ============================

### Lấy danh sách sách
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/books
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Lấy sách ID=1
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Thêm sách mới
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Python 101",
  "author": "Mike"
}

###

### Xóa sách ID=1
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/books/1



### ============================
### VERSION 2 - Uniform Interface
### ============================

### Lấy danh sách sách
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v2/books
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Lấy sách cụ thể
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v2/books/2
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Thêm sách mới
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v2/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Fluent Python",
  "author": "Luciano Ramalho"
}

###

### Sửa thông tin sách (PUT - chuẩn Uniform Interface)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v2/books/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Fluent Python - 2nd Edition",
  "author": "Luciano Ramalho"
}

###

### Xóa sách
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v2/books/2



### ============================
### VERSION 3 - Stateless
### ============================

### Lấy token đăng nhập (stateless JWT)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v3/books/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "kiet"
}

###

### Lấy danh sách sách (yêu cầu token)
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v3/books
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Thêm sách mới (yêu cầu token)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v3/books
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Designing Data-Intensive Applications",
  "author": "Martin Kleppmann"
}



### ============================
### VERSION 4 - Cacheable + Full RESTful + Evaluation
### ============================

### Lấy danh sách (có Cache-Control)
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v4/books
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Lấy sách ID=1
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v4/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Thêm sách mới
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v4/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Deep Learning with Python",
  "author": "François Chollet"
}

###

### Xóa sách ID=2
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v4/books/2
Content-Type: application/json
